{"tid":52310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］有冇人屋企係用Samsung 電子鎖~?","createTime":"2016-12-24T03:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T03:54:14.000Z","uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"feaed974c4fa125ab18bf1dd4661b9ffb702c250","tid":52310,"uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"頭先出門口嘅時候唔小心㩒左防盜制, 即係如果有人係屋內開門就會響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上左車家人先WhatsApp 我話我反鎖左, 有冇方法佢自己解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b54526ccb2761504c4411945273533859a1cac2","tid":52310,"uid":29585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"比翻個屋企人啦"},{"pid":"1025ff468987d6d161fcf101b0a760ace976c2f6","tid":52310,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"用鎖匙？"},{"pid":"f69dcebe4afd0eea566e9f1df86bfb786ae8d7fc","tid":52310,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"搵消防"},{"pid":"76b24b96939129e3afdad1a725c4708e23881397","tid":52310,"uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比翻個屋企人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係咩意思~?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54caf9ed2fd7e3814189e129586945c88200b7de","tid":52310,"uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用鎖匙？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢係屋內, 好似得門外先有鎖鑰窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7ee3e6d46a88faf0a74b0c7fb268d7dbf68f86","tid":52310,"uid":28112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比翻個屋企人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係咩意思~?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos