10,"uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢攞條鎖匙後門出去，返前門開門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n那有後門, 開唔到鎖今晚就比人插後門啦~"},{"pid":"4498048706403b53f694cd33845351a45dd21568","tid":52310,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"爬窗落樓 搭番lift上黎係出面開門囉"},{"pid":"39784a88c674e4ea10cb5c2779fe5b84dffe497a","tid":52310,"uid":32016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爬窗落樓 搭番lift上黎係出面開門囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住中層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋如果係我比人反鎖我都可能會考慮下咁做, 但屋入面果個係我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62790e94bb539a638c1d8a88c60e47ebbf47a44d","tid":52310,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比翻個屋企人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係咩意思~?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}